    "description": "<p>By the Community; For the Community; With the Community.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Loving Heart Multi-Service Centre (LHMSC) is a Social Service Agency (SSA) that provides services to families, elderly residents, and needy people living in the South West District of Singapore, with particular focus on the Yuhua and Jurong East communities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>What differentiates us from other SSAs is our anthropological approach towards social issues and working with the local community to address service gaps through design thinking and other structured methodologies.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Besides being an SSA, LHMSC is also &nbsp;the first volunteer centre in Singapore appointed to coordinate volunteerism within Jurong East Town.&nbsp;</p>",
